1
00:00:11,160 --> 00:00:12,790
(You Chen'an set up a trap)

2
00:00:12,839 --> 00:00:14,110
(and You Longsheng died.)

3
00:00:14,610 --> 00:00:16,690
(The peaceful negotiation
took an unexpected turn.)

4
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:18,349
(The situation turned tense once again.)

5
00:00:20,079 --> 00:00:22,029
(The herbs
promised by Nanzhao did not arrive.)

6
00:00:22,399 --> 00:00:24,150
(The lives of the remaining people)

7
00:00:24,239 --> 00:00:25,549
(were in danger.)

8
00:00:26,039 --> 00:00:27,549
(You Chen'an captured by father)

9
00:00:27,550 --> 00:00:28,990
(and threatened us to go to Nanzhao.)

10
00:00:29,399 --> 00:00:30,590
(I had to obey.)

11
00:00:31,600 --> 00:00:33,690
(King of Nanzhao's illness
suddenly turned serious.)

12
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:35,520
(You Chen'an ruled the kingdom
in his place.)

13
00:00:35,620 --> 00:00:38,500
(He claimed he only wanted
to have peaceful negotiations with Great Tang)

14
00:00:39,200 --> 00:00:40,829
(but from my understanding of him,)

15
00:00:41,439 --> 00:00:43,189
(things wouldn't be as simple as that.)

16
00:00:44,500 --> 00:00:46,520
(I hope His Highness
wouldn't be threatened by him)

17
00:00:46,719 --> 00:00:48,189
(for my sake.)

18
00:01:02,000 --> 00:01:07,270
♪Embark on a farewell
without saying goodbye♪

19
00:01:07,480 --> 00:01:12,030
♪Build a bridge between life and death♪

20
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:16,310
♪Hear a voiceless declaration♪

21
00:01:16,520 --> 00:01:21,510
♪Break disguises, cross illusions♪

22
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:24,279
♪A fleeting life and delusions♪

23
00:01:24,280 --> 00:01:27,119
♪The surface always conceals♪

24
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:32,310
♪Separate cause and effect♪

25
00:01:32,560 --> 00:01:35,039
♪A twisted path, rising and falling♪

26
00:01:35,040 --> 00:01:37,679
♪Seek the path amid the hazy unknown♪

27
00:01:37,680 --> 00:01:42,519
♪Writing oblivion with a sharp blade♪

28
00:01:42,520 --> 00:01:47,550
♪No matter how far, I gaze at the light♪

29
00:01:47,760 --> 00:01:53,110
♪Fearing no wild lands, I press on♪

30
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:58,590
♪To see the tides of the world
once more♪

31
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:03,870
♪The deeper truth is buried, it grows♪

32
00:02:04,080 --> 00:02:06,230
♪Until it is set free♪

33
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:20,679
=The Imperial Coroner S2=
(Adapted from Idle Girl's The Constable's Wife)

34
00:02:20,680 --> 00:02:23,759
(This story is entirely fictional.)

35
00:02:23,760 --> 00:02:26,590
=Episode 28=

36
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,390
There's no peaceful negotiation

37
00:02:28,400 --> 00:02:30,190
unless they're willing
to give us an account!

38
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,309
Second Prince,
you may be able to withstand it,

39
00:02:32,680 --> 00:02:34,189
but my soldiers and I

40
00:02:34,560 --> 00:02:35,990
cannot withstand it!

41
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,110
Great General,

42
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,810
you've been
running your mouth many times,

43
00:02:42,479 --> 00:02:44,349
but I've never punished you for it.

44
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,438
These Great Tang envoys

45
00:02:46,439 --> 00:02:48,670
came here because I invited them

46
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:51,550
yet you keep trying to stir up trouble.

47
00:02:51,960 --> 00:02:53,909
Are you worried
that there might be no war

48
00:02:54,159 --> 00:02:55,710
for you to take credit from?

49
00:02:55,759 --> 00:02:56,390
You...

50
00:02:56,680 --> 00:02:57,589
Great General.

51
00:02:59,199 --> 00:03:01,630
If the relationship between
the two states is ruined by you,

52
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:04,430
can you bear this grave crime?

53
00:03:05,639 --> 00:03:07,950
Even if I don't punish you,

54
00:03:09,680 --> 00:03:12,189
how do you
explain yourself to Great Tang?

55
00:03:15,240 --> 00:03:16,869
Second Prince, you must be joking.

56
00:03:16,900 --> 00:03:19,869
Nanzhao's internal affairs
are not related to the peaceful negotiations.

57
00:03:20,000 --> 00:03:22,789
Great Tang will never meddle
in Nanzhao's internal affairs.

58
00:03:23,780 --> 00:03:25,749
Moreover, there's more
to Eldest Prince's death

59
00:03:25,800 --> 00:03:27,069
than meets the eye.

60
00:03:27,199 --> 00:03:29,909
Second Prince, please uncover the truth
as soon as possible.

61
00:03:32,800 --> 00:03:35,430
The envoys of Great Tang are polite.

62
00:03:36,159 --> 00:03:37,270
Second Prince,

63
00:03:37,330 --> 00:03:38,990
if you want to begin peaceful negotiations,

64
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:41,580
you should either wait until the King
recovers from his illness

65
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,909
or

66
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:45,309
until the cause
of Eldest Prince's death is uncovered

67
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,198
so no one else will doubt you.

68
00:03:47,199 --> 00:03:50,150
- Yes, the Great General has a point.
- Yes, the Great General has a point.

69
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:58,189
Since there are objections
among the palace officials,

70
00:03:59,479 --> 00:04:00,670
I'll have to trouble

71
00:04:00,750 --> 00:04:02,950
the envoys of Great Tang
to stay in the palace for now.

72
00:04:04,199 --> 00:04:05,990
When my father feels better,

73
00:04:06,390 --> 00:04:08,309
we will continue
with the peaceful negotiations.

74
00:04:09,599 --> 00:04:10,550
Prime Minister.

75
00:04:10,599 --> 00:04:11,390
Yes.

76
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:14,950
Send all the envoys
to rest in the side hall.

77
00:04:15,439 --> 00:04:16,270
Yes.

78
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,190
Father,

79
00:04:19,680 --> 00:04:20,710
let's go back and rest.

80
00:04:54,399 --> 00:04:55,229
Commandery Prince An.

81
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:56,950
Take a seat.

82
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:03,789
I remember we had
a thrilling game at Weiguo Temple.

83
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:06,229
Unfortunately, I've not met

84
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:08,039
an opponent like you

85
00:05:08,040 --> 00:05:09,669
since I came back to Nanzhao.

86
00:05:11,680 --> 00:05:12,870
Commandery Prince An,

87
00:05:13,000 --> 00:05:14,429
I wonder if you can

88
00:05:14,639 --> 00:05:16,109
play another game with me today.

89
00:05:17,759 --> 00:05:19,349
A good player plays for the momentum.

90
00:05:20,000 --> 00:05:21,660
A bad player plays
to capture the pieces.

91
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,229
Second Prince, your game

92
00:05:23,519 --> 00:05:25,630
has no advantage in
timing, terrain, and people.

93
00:05:25,839 --> 00:05:27,750
You only depend on some trickery.

94
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:29,950
It's difficult for people
to play this game with you.

95
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,310
Even if it's trickery, so what?

96
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,630
As long as it's useful.

97
00:05:35,040 --> 00:05:38,390
You, for example, Commandery Prince An,
you knew this was a treacherous place

98
00:05:38,439 --> 00:05:40,750
yet you still came for Chu Chu.

99
00:05:41,279 --> 00:05:42,318
Where are they?

100
00:05:42,319 --> 00:05:44,310
Chu Chu and I are mentor and disciple.

101
00:05:45,240 --> 00:05:46,830
I won't hurt them easily.

102
00:05:47,199 --> 00:05:48,710
It doesn't seem like

103
00:05:49,000 --> 00:05:51,029
you lured me to Nanzhao
for a peaceful negotiation.

104
00:06:03,279 --> 00:06:04,789
As you can see,

105
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:07,670
I'm not the one
who doesn't want a peaceful negotiation.

106
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:09,390
The Great General and the rest

107
00:06:09,639 --> 00:06:10,950
are keeping a close eye on me.

108
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:14,109
They are worried
that I might get more merit

109
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,029
while my father is gravely ill.

110
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,549
They lead many soldiers.

111
00:06:18,800 --> 00:06:20,190
If they are in power,

112
00:06:21,040 --> 00:06:23,429
I'm sure you know what will happen.

113
00:06:23,759 --> 00:06:25,429
You are alone

114
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:27,190
and can't win over everyone.

115
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:30,469
You lured me here
because you wanted to use Great Tang

116
00:06:30,480 --> 00:06:31,789
to inherit the throne.

117
00:06:32,600 --> 00:06:34,150
We are just using each other.

118
00:06:35,879 --> 00:06:37,390
If I inherit the throne successfully,

119
00:06:38,079 --> 00:06:40,630
I will form an alliance
with Great Tang immediately

120
00:06:41,399 --> 00:06:42,789
and give benefits to Great Tang.

121
00:06:44,199 --> 00:06:45,349
Commandery Prince An,

122
00:06:45,590 --> 00:06:46,669
I hope you consider it well

123
00:06:46,800 --> 00:06:48,880
for personal reasons
and the benefits of the kingdom.

124
00:06:56,519 --> 00:06:58,029
According to the law of Great Tang,

125
00:06:58,839 --> 00:07:01,150
a decree will be issued

126
00:07:01,240 --> 00:07:02,630
upon the death of any tribal leader

127
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,750
to instill the successor.

128
00:07:05,079 --> 00:07:06,390
After the tribal chief dies,

129
00:07:06,439 --> 00:07:08,469
Great Tang will choose the successor

130
00:07:08,560 --> 00:07:09,950
and re-confer the title.

131
00:07:10,720 --> 00:07:12,710
Right now,
the King of Nanzhao is just ill.

132
00:07:13,439 --> 00:07:15,989
If Great Tang is going
to confer the title forcefully,

133
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,950
the position

134
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:19,349
is still not legitimate.

135
00:07:19,800 --> 00:07:21,150
Then...

136
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,349
If my father

137
00:07:26,120 --> 00:07:26,909
is...

138
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:36,710
Then, I will inform His Majesty about this

139
00:07:36,959 --> 00:07:39,078
to ensure the peace
and stability of both states.

140
00:07:39,079 --> 00:07:41,800
However, this has nothing to do
with Chu Chu and my father-in-law.

141
00:07:42,040 --> 00:07:43,510
Release them first.

142
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:44,589
Commandery Prince An,

143
00:07:45,920 --> 00:07:47,109
both of us know

144
00:07:47,330 --> 00:07:49,270
there's no room for negotiation
regarding this.

145
00:07:51,079 --> 00:07:52,630
However, to show my sincerity,

146
00:07:53,090 --> 00:07:55,229
I will send your father-in-law
back to Jiaozhou first.

147
00:07:55,959 --> 00:07:57,669
If I inherit the throne successfully,

148
00:07:58,279 --> 00:07:59,589
I will get someone

149
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:02,669
to send Chu Chu
back to your side safely.

150
00:08:20,879 --> 00:08:21,830
Who is it?

151
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:29,310
Official Li?

152
00:08:29,639 --> 00:08:30,950
What a coincidence.

153
00:08:34,399 --> 00:08:36,470
Former commandant of the Shence Army,

154
00:08:36,759 --> 00:08:37,789
Zhou Han.

155
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,829
Have you forgotten?

156
00:08:39,279 --> 00:08:40,479
We used to

157
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:42,630
serve Duke Chang.

158
00:08:42,799 --> 00:08:43,630
Right now,

159
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,429
we are both serving Nanzhao.

160
00:08:45,440 --> 00:08:46,678
Don't you think we are fated?

161
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:47,309
Shut up.

162
00:08:50,879 --> 00:08:52,230
Don't mention this again.

163
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:57,359
What are you doing?

164
00:08:57,360 --> 00:08:59,870
I'm just here to send you a message.

165
00:09:03,519 --> 00:09:04,990
When one is no longer useful,

166
00:09:05,200 --> 00:09:06,510
he will be killed.

167
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,949
Commandery Prince An

168
00:09:09,000 --> 00:09:11,669
is inviting you to meet him.

169
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:17,750
Why so serious?

170
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:19,110
Smile.

171
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:26,150
Zhou Han is really deceiving.

172
00:09:28,559 --> 00:09:29,390
Tell me.

173
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:32,390
If I try to seek credit
from Second Prince with this,

174
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:35,230
can you still escape from the palace?

175
00:09:37,080 --> 00:09:37,909
Li Zhang,

176
00:09:38,879 --> 00:09:40,630
you know clearly

177
00:09:40,660 --> 00:09:43,360
that Great Tang and Nanzhao's
peaceful negotiations will happen soon.

178
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:46,750
The day You Chen'an
inherits the throne officially

179
00:09:47,240 --> 00:09:49,270
will be the day you die.

180
00:09:50,279 --> 00:09:51,230
Xiao Jinyu,

181
00:09:51,559 --> 00:09:52,558
stop acting

182
00:09:52,559 --> 00:09:54,350
all high and mighty before me.

183
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:57,510
You are smart and scheme
with flawless precision.

184
00:09:57,759 --> 00:09:58,709
So what?

185
00:09:59,080 --> 00:10:00,669
You are still trapped here.

186
00:10:02,799 --> 00:10:04,429
How can you be so sure

187
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:07,069
that You Chen'an will kill me?

188
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:23,789
Master Chu has returned
to his residence in Jiaozhou.

189
00:10:24,039 --> 00:10:26,230
You can just
rest here at ease, Your Highness.

190
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:27,949
I'll be waiting at the entrance.

191
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:30,390
If you need anything, please call me.

192
00:10:48,399 --> 00:10:48,949
Let's go.

193
00:10:50,039 --> 00:10:52,309
His Highness said everything is ready.

194
00:10:56,519 --> 00:10:58,230
It's late at night.

195
00:10:58,399 --> 00:11:01,350
Where are you
taking the Princess Consort, Lady Jing?

196
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:09,709
Leave first.

197
00:11:10,159 --> 00:11:11,350
Go back and tell His Highness

198
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,230
that I'm fine.

199
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:15,110
That's right.

200
00:11:15,519 --> 00:11:16,949
Go back and rest early

201
00:11:17,279 --> 00:11:18,590
so you don't get injured.

202
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:20,669
Someone,

203
00:11:21,159 --> 00:11:23,630
bring Lady Jing back to rest.

204
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:24,669
Chu Chu.

205
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,638
Go.

206
00:11:25,639 --> 00:11:26,990
Don't worry. I'll be fine.

207
00:11:34,840 --> 00:11:35,669
Second Prince,

208
00:11:36,240 --> 00:11:37,599
this place attracts attention.

209
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:38,999
Why not send them there

210
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:40,189
to be guarded together

211
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,309
so nothing can go wrong?

212
00:11:43,159 --> 00:11:44,549
Let's do as you say.

213
00:11:46,159 --> 00:11:46,829
Someone,

214
00:11:46,879 --> 00:11:47,549
bring her away.

215
00:11:50,159 --> 00:11:50,949
Li Zhang.

216
00:11:54,279 --> 00:11:55,390
As for

217
00:11:56,159 --> 00:11:56,990
that person,

218
00:11:58,399 --> 00:11:59,390
you may do it now.

219
00:11:59,960 --> 00:12:00,990
It's time.

220
00:12:02,600 --> 00:12:03,510
Second Prince.

221
00:12:04,390 --> 00:12:05,709
Make sure to leave no loose ends.

222
00:12:08,159 --> 00:12:09,069
Go.

223
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,789
This way.

224
00:12:34,799 --> 00:12:37,398
Don't try to use me
to threaten Commandery Prince An.

225
00:12:37,399 --> 00:12:40,510
He will never sacrifice
the benefits of Great Tang for my sake.

226
00:12:42,039 --> 00:12:43,750
That's out of your control.

227
00:12:44,039 --> 00:12:44,829
Your Highness.

228
00:12:45,720 --> 00:12:46,870
Letter from Jinli.

229
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,949
Master Chu has arrived in Jiaozhou.

230
00:12:51,759 --> 00:12:53,949
You Chen'an is acting kindly.

231
00:12:53,960 --> 00:12:55,119
He released Master Chu

232
00:12:55,120 --> 00:12:57,470
but trapped us and Chu Chu in the palace

233
00:12:57,519 --> 00:12:59,750
with the excuse of protecting us.

234
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:05,429
He's not wrong.

235
00:13:06,039 --> 00:13:07,429
Compared to us,

236
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:10,110
he is more worried
about us dying in Nanzhao.

237
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:11,829
You are right.

238
00:13:12,840 --> 00:13:14,909
Otherwise, you wouldn't have
asked Yue to go.

239
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,829
Get out.

240
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,470
Father!

241
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,069
You left

242
00:13:41,399 --> 00:13:44,549
and abandon me and the people of Nanzhao
before you achieve your ambition!

243
00:13:50,639 --> 00:13:52,230
What are you doing, Great General?

244
00:13:52,600 --> 00:13:54,510
My father just passed away

245
00:13:54,520 --> 00:13:55,990
and you're already disrespecting him.

246
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,309
I just want to confirm
the King's cause of death.

247
00:13:58,440 --> 00:13:59,750
Second Prince,

248
00:13:59,799 --> 00:14:02,350
why did you transfer the King
to the underground palace?

249
00:14:06,120 --> 00:14:06,909
Li Zhang.

250
00:14:07,120 --> 00:14:07,909
Yes.

251
00:14:08,240 --> 00:14:10,278
I asked you to find a sealed place

252
00:14:10,279 --> 00:14:11,990
and look after Father.

253
00:14:12,399 --> 00:14:13,999
Why did you make your own decision

254
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:15,669
and placed my father here?

255
00:14:17,440 --> 00:14:18,789
Do you know your crime?

256
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,429
Second Prince, calm down.

257
00:14:21,480 --> 00:14:23,110
Second Prince, spare me.

258
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:25,439
This is the most sealed place
in the whole place.

259
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:26,590
It is also very quiet.

260
00:14:26,720 --> 00:14:27,390
This...

261
00:14:27,480 --> 00:14:29,350
It's most suitable
for the King to recuperate.

262
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:31,160
Second Prince,
please investigate it clearly.

263
00:14:32,039 --> 00:14:33,470
You might be considerate,

264
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:36,309
but you still failed to treat Father.

265
00:14:36,879 --> 00:14:38,230
You'll be given a serious demerit.

266
00:14:39,120 --> 00:14:41,270
I'll deal with you in the future.

267
00:14:45,559 --> 00:14:46,510
Great General.

268
00:14:48,399 --> 00:14:49,669
Do you have other questions?

269
00:14:49,799 --> 00:14:52,069
The King has been healthy.

270
00:14:52,364 --> 00:14:55,029
Why would he pass away
after suffering a stroke for a few days?

271
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:58,479
I'm afraid
that something fishy is going on.

272
00:14:58,480 --> 00:14:59,359
Great General,

273
00:14:59,360 --> 00:15:01,949
I think you don't care
about my father's cause of death.

274
00:15:03,440 --> 00:15:05,549
You intend to start a rebellion.

275
00:15:05,559 --> 00:15:06,309
You...

276
00:15:06,919 --> 00:15:08,150
You are falsely accusing me!

277
00:15:10,919 --> 00:15:12,558
I risked my whole life

278
00:15:12,559 --> 00:15:13,549
for Nanzhao.

279
00:15:13,559 --> 00:15:15,549
I'm loyal. How would I rebel?

280
00:15:18,360 --> 00:15:19,990
Risked your whole life

281
00:15:20,000 --> 00:15:21,270
for the state?

282
00:15:22,399 --> 00:15:25,750
Great General, Are you trying to use
your achievements to excuse your mistakes?

283
00:15:26,279 --> 00:15:28,479
You keep slandering me

284
00:15:28,480 --> 00:15:29,949
because you want to get rid of me

285
00:15:30,120 --> 00:15:33,398
before taking over Nanzhao and holding
its military authority to protect yourself.

286
00:15:33,399 --> 00:15:34,110
You...

287
00:15:34,120 --> 00:15:35,479
You schemed for personal gain,

288
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:36,599
framed a prince,

289
00:15:36,600 --> 00:15:37,829
and intended to rebel.

290
00:15:38,440 --> 00:15:39,429
Capture him.

291
00:15:42,520 --> 00:15:44,319
I see. You've planned this
for a long time.

292
00:15:44,320 --> 00:15:46,630
You must be the one
who caused the King's death!

293
00:15:46,759 --> 00:15:48,429
Take him away!

294
00:15:48,879 --> 00:15:49,949
Quickly!

295
00:15:53,919 --> 00:15:54,870
Second Prince,

296
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:56,719
please inherit the throne immediately,

297
00:15:56,720 --> 00:15:57,909
take charge,

298
00:15:58,120 --> 00:15:59,510
and restore the state's foundation.

299
00:16:02,039 --> 00:16:03,270
Now that it has come to this,

300
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,350
I have no choice.

301
00:17:02,399 --> 00:17:03,878
Congratulations, My King.

302
00:17:03,879 --> 00:17:05,990
- Congratulations, My King.
- Congratulations, My King.

303
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,350
Pass down my order.

304
00:17:10,559 --> 00:17:11,909
Any rebels

305
00:17:13,060 --> 00:17:14,110
will be killed immediately.

306
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:15,870
Yes.

307
00:17:39,160 --> 00:17:41,150
I heard you were very worried.

308
00:17:41,559 --> 00:17:43,070
I purposely came to visit you.

309
00:17:45,640 --> 00:17:46,749
Have you

310
00:17:47,160 --> 00:17:48,070
inherited the throne?

311
00:17:50,079 --> 00:17:51,669
My father passed away suddenly.

312
00:17:52,160 --> 00:17:54,669
For the benefits and stability
of Nanzhao and Great Tang,

313
00:17:54,700 --> 00:17:56,790
I have no choice
but to take over political matters.

314
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:59,669
Right now, I'm waiting for
the investiture of Great Tang's emperor.

315
00:18:00,079 --> 00:18:01,709
Then, my position will be legitimate.

316
00:18:03,759 --> 00:18:05,669
The King of Nanzhao suddenly passed away

317
00:18:05,670 --> 00:18:07,600
when he was
confined in the underground palace?

318
00:18:07,839 --> 00:18:09,269
The scheme about his death

319
00:18:09,599 --> 00:18:11,390
will soon come to light.

320
00:18:11,799 --> 00:18:15,110
I will decide how the history books
of Nanzhao should be written.

321
00:18:16,083 --> 00:18:18,233
I am the only heir
left behind by Father.

322
00:18:18,640 --> 00:18:21,110
The treacherous officials
who tried to usurp the throne

323
00:18:21,599 --> 00:18:23,189
have been captured.

324
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:25,580
Would the Great Tang
turn its back on rightful authority?

325
00:18:26,319 --> 00:18:29,310
I'll also promise Commandery Prince An
to return you

326
00:18:29,440 --> 00:18:31,189
once the decree from Great Tang is here.

327
00:18:31,480 --> 00:18:33,509
Are you using me
to force His Highness to obey?

328
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:36,150
Do you think
your plan will go so smoothly?

329
00:18:36,160 --> 00:18:38,380
His Highness will never
do things unfairly for my sake.

330
00:18:38,480 --> 00:18:39,949
He will also not do as you wish.

331
00:18:40,680 --> 00:18:41,989
Actually, I came here

332
00:18:42,119 --> 00:18:43,630
to thank you.

333
00:18:44,279 --> 00:18:46,429
Thinking back
to when I was in Great Tang,

334
00:18:46,440 --> 00:18:49,150
if you and Commandery Prince An
hadn't saved me

335
00:18:49,279 --> 00:18:51,229
and appointed me
to the Three Judicial Offices,

336
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:52,830
I would've

337
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:55,719
died in a foreign state
with my body in the wilderness now.

338
00:18:55,720 --> 00:18:57,429
It's my fault for saving you.

339
00:19:01,480 --> 00:19:02,989
No matter how you see me,

340
00:19:03,759 --> 00:19:05,630
I'll also see you as my mentor.

341
00:19:06,200 --> 00:19:07,229
Without you,

342
00:19:07,559 --> 00:19:09,110
I won't be myself today.

343
00:19:09,440 --> 00:19:10,429
You Chen'an.

344
00:19:11,039 --> 00:19:12,469
What goes around, comes around.

345
00:19:12,799 --> 00:19:14,310
Those who do bad things

346
00:19:14,440 --> 00:19:16,229
will not end well.

347
00:19:16,599 --> 00:19:18,229
What goes around, comes around.

348
00:19:19,319 --> 00:19:20,630
But what I'm doing

349
00:19:21,200 --> 00:19:22,630
is the will of Heaven.

350
00:19:23,839 --> 00:19:24,909
Both our lives

351
00:19:25,359 --> 00:19:27,310
are in my hands.

352
00:19:40,380 --> 00:19:41,909
The new king has inherited the throne.

353
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:44,350
Since the food yesterday
didn't suit all of your taste buds,

354
00:19:44,640 --> 00:19:47,830
His Majesty purposely ordered
that Chang'an dishes be made today.

355
00:19:55,160 --> 00:19:56,590
This is Chu Chu's.

356
00:19:56,960 --> 00:19:58,150
Why do you have it?

357
00:19:58,960 --> 00:19:59,630
Speak.

358
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:00,870
What did you do to Chu Chu?

359
00:20:02,960 --> 00:20:05,550
The King wants Commandery
Princess Consort An to stay longer.

360
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:07,509
She won't be needing these for now

361
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:09,949
so the King asked me to return these things.

362
00:20:12,160 --> 00:20:14,909
The King asked me to deliver a message.

363
00:20:15,319 --> 00:20:16,830
The former king has passed away.

364
00:20:16,850 --> 00:20:19,239
The day Great Tang issued the decree
to appoint the new king

365
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:22,150
is the day Commandery Princess Consort An
will return to Jiaozhou.

366
00:20:23,319 --> 00:20:26,269
The King of Nanzhao died a timely death.

367
00:20:26,480 --> 00:20:28,189
If these dishes

368
00:20:28,200 --> 00:20:30,150
still don't suit your taste buds,

369
00:20:30,480 --> 00:20:31,429
The King

370
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:32,989
will serve a feast

371
00:20:33,359 --> 00:20:34,749
for all of you.

372
00:20:37,500 --> 00:20:39,520
I will send a letter
to His Majesty immediately.

373
00:20:39,839 --> 00:20:41,030
Within three days,

374
00:20:41,440 --> 00:20:43,310
the decree will surely arrive in Nanzhao.

375
00:20:44,279 --> 00:20:45,989
However, if something happens to Chu Chu,

376
00:20:46,839 --> 00:20:49,150
I will make You Chen'an pay.

377
00:20:49,319 --> 00:20:51,070
Commandery Prince An, don't worry.

378
00:21:12,960 --> 00:21:13,749
My King,

379
00:21:13,960 --> 00:21:15,159
the envoy of Great Tang,

380
00:21:15,160 --> 00:21:16,880
Commandery Prince An,
Xiao Jinyu, is here.

381
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:18,909
Summon him.

382
00:21:23,000 --> 00:21:23,669
Summon

383
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:25,989
the envoy of Great Tang to the hall.

384
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,199
The golden seal glittered,

385
00:21:37,200 --> 00:21:38,630
its brilliance unmatched.

386
00:21:38,720 --> 00:21:40,989
The emperor of Great Tang's grace
is upon Nanzhao.

387
00:21:41,440 --> 00:21:42,830
Heaven grants the ruler authority,

388
00:21:43,119 --> 00:21:44,590
legitimacy is declared,

389
00:21:44,890 --> 00:21:46,229
and the golden seal is conferred.

390
00:21:46,286 --> 00:21:48,916
Nanzhao remains united in purpose
and virtue with the Great Tang,

391
00:21:48,920 --> 00:21:50,358
obeys Great Tang's orders,

392
00:21:50,359 --> 00:21:51,830
protect its territory,

393
00:21:52,079 --> 00:21:53,550
and visits Nanzhao

394
00:21:53,759 --> 00:21:55,269
every year in court.

395
00:22:23,119 --> 00:22:24,070
Xiao Jinyu,

396
00:22:26,759 --> 00:22:27,949
what's the meaning of this?

397
00:22:28,319 --> 00:22:29,669
You Chen'an!

398
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:51,880
Treacherous son
who killed your mother, brother

399
00:22:51,890 --> 00:22:53,949
and your father to usurp the throne!

400
00:22:53,950 --> 00:22:56,350
How dare you be so preposterous
as to accept Heaven's will?

401
00:22:57,640 --> 00:22:59,469
What does the King mean

402
00:22:59,500 --> 00:23:00,838
by killing his father and brother?

403
00:23:00,839 --> 00:23:01,870
How would I know?

404
00:23:08,240 --> 00:23:09,429
Xiao Jinyu,

405
00:23:10,559 --> 00:23:12,310
you are so daring.

406
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:15,709
The Great Tang is trying
to destabilize Nanzhao.

407
00:23:16,319 --> 00:23:19,630
How dare you get an impostor here?

408
00:23:20,559 --> 00:23:21,590
Someone,

409
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,390
capture him!

410
00:23:23,640 --> 00:23:24,989
Who dares to do it!

411
00:23:26,200 --> 00:23:27,749
Where's the Luojuzi Army?

412
00:23:36,400 --> 00:23:37,989
It's the king indeed!

413
00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:39,598
The King has revived!

414
00:23:39,599 --> 00:23:41,310
It is Nanzhao's blessing indeed.

415
00:23:41,480 --> 00:23:43,150
Greetings, My King!

416
00:23:44,319 --> 00:23:47,269
- Greetings, My King!
- Greetings, My King!

417
00:23:50,559 --> 00:23:51,630
Xiao Jinyu,

418
00:23:52,839 --> 00:23:54,070
are you going

419
00:23:54,920 --> 00:23:56,390
to let Chu Chu die?

420
00:23:58,390 --> 00:24:00,110
That's none of your concern,
Second Prince.

421
00:24:00,917 --> 00:24:02,666
Li Zhang is probably on his way here

422
00:24:02,799 --> 00:24:04,269
with Chu Chu.

423
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,429
Li Zhang.

424
00:24:11,039 --> 00:24:12,429
Li Zhang, where are you?

425
00:24:12,759 --> 00:24:14,590
Li Zhang saw you

426
00:24:15,079 --> 00:24:16,390
kill your mother,

427
00:24:16,400 --> 00:24:17,310
your brother,

428
00:24:17,519 --> 00:24:18,550
and your father

429
00:24:18,599 --> 00:24:19,550
to usurp the throne.

430
00:24:20,079 --> 00:24:21,269
Of course, he knows

431
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:23,310
you won't keep him alive for too long.

432
00:24:23,320 --> 00:24:26,120
When I promised to let him atone
for his crimes for doing a great deed,

433
00:24:26,440 --> 00:24:28,110
he did not hesitate for too long.

434
00:24:28,880 --> 00:24:29,830
Tell me.

435
00:24:30,039 --> 00:24:31,229
What do you need me to do?

436
00:24:32,279 --> 00:24:34,509
To be conferred the title
as soon as possible,

437
00:24:34,800 --> 00:24:37,180
You Chen'an will surely
ask you to kill the king of Nanzhao.

438
00:24:37,359 --> 00:24:38,269
That person,

439
00:24:38,400 --> 00:24:39,429
you may do it now.

440
00:24:39,839 --> 00:24:41,030
It's time.

441
00:24:42,519 --> 00:24:43,949
I want you to find an opportunity

442
00:24:44,680 --> 00:24:46,509
to put Chu Chu

443
00:24:46,839 --> 00:24:48,310
and the King of Nanzhao together.

444
00:24:52,450 --> 00:24:54,118
I've been ordered
by Commandery Prince An

445
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:55,229
to assist Your Highness

446
00:24:55,279 --> 00:24:56,469
and save the King of Nanzhao.

447
00:24:56,920 --> 00:24:57,830
He said

448
00:24:57,920 --> 00:24:59,350
he believed you should still remember

449
00:24:59,400 --> 00:25:01,709
how to fake the King of Nanzhao's death.

450
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:05,749
I had a discussion with Chu Chu

451
00:25:05,799 --> 00:25:07,949
about your fake death.

452
00:25:08,480 --> 00:25:11,110
So, if Chu Chu
can approach the King of Nanzhao,

453
00:25:11,240 --> 00:25:13,598
it's not easy to put him

454
00:25:13,599 --> 00:25:14,949
in a temporary state of shock.

455
00:25:15,839 --> 00:25:16,949
The difficult thing

456
00:25:17,319 --> 00:25:21,278
is getting you to leave immediately
after confirming the king's death.

457
00:25:21,279 --> 00:25:22,838
(Airway blocked,
with induced cardiac arrest.)

458
00:25:22,839 --> 00:25:24,310
Because the fake death condition

459
00:25:24,519 --> 00:25:27,150
can only be maintained
for half an hour by using this method.

460
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:29,719
You've planned this for a long time.

461
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:31,199
- I predicted
- You caused the King's death!

462
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:34,358
you'd be elated by the news
of the King of Nanzhao's passing

463
00:25:34,359 --> 00:25:36,060
and take over
military command immediately.

464
00:25:36,240 --> 00:25:38,110
You'd build your authority
within the palace

465
00:25:39,799 --> 00:25:43,269
and neglected the King's body.

466
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:45,669
Your Highness,

467
00:25:45,799 --> 00:25:47,199
from his pulse,

468
00:25:47,200 --> 00:25:49,509
the toxic energy has been expelled.

469
00:25:49,519 --> 00:25:50,550
In two days,

470
00:25:50,559 --> 00:25:51,518
the King of Nanzhao

471
00:25:51,519 --> 00:25:52,949
will recover.

472
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:59,318
You Chen'an killed his mother, brother,

473
00:25:59,319 --> 00:26:00,830
and father to usurp the throne.

474
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:02,150
Those who were blinded

475
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:03,910
and are willing
to reflect on their mistakes

476
00:26:03,920 --> 00:26:05,310
will be spared from their crimes.

477
00:26:05,400 --> 00:26:06,150
If anyone

478
00:26:06,240 --> 00:26:07,669
decides to resist,

479
00:26:08,279 --> 00:26:10,989
they will be punished
with the same crime as You Chen'an.

480
00:26:11,039 --> 00:26:13,030
We were worried about Nanzhao's safety

481
00:26:13,190 --> 00:26:14,229
and were blinded

482
00:26:14,519 --> 00:26:15,909
by  Second Prince accidentally.

483
00:26:16,039 --> 00:26:17,219
My King, please forgive us.

484
00:26:17,220 --> 00:26:19,610
- My King, please forgive us.
- My King, please forgive us.

485
00:26:24,799 --> 00:26:25,909
Great.

486
00:26:28,039 --> 00:26:29,390
I knew

487
00:26:31,599 --> 00:26:34,229
all of you would betray me.

488
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:37,709
Everyone.

489
00:26:41,160 --> 00:26:42,630
You Chen'an,

490
00:26:43,400 --> 00:26:44,838
I thought

491
00:26:44,839 --> 00:26:47,278
making you doubt
and compete with Longsheng

492
00:26:47,279 --> 00:26:48,399
all these years

493
00:26:48,400 --> 00:26:50,989
would make you two grow quickly.

494
00:26:51,559 --> 00:26:53,550
In the end, I didn't expect

495
00:26:55,240 --> 00:26:57,118
myself to become a pawn

496
00:26:57,119 --> 00:26:59,310
you could sacrifice.

497
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:03,070
After all,

498
00:27:03,160 --> 00:27:05,269
I'm also at fault for this.

499
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:07,709
We are father-and-son after all.

500
00:27:08,119 --> 00:27:09,630
If you reflect on your mistake now,

501
00:27:10,200 --> 00:27:12,390
I will spare your life

502
00:27:12,960 --> 00:27:15,030
because of our relationship.

503
00:27:18,319 --> 00:27:19,310
Father and son?

504
00:27:22,160 --> 00:27:24,110
How dare you mention our relationship?

505
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:29,479
How dare you call yourself my father

506
00:27:29,480 --> 00:27:31,669
when you disowned me and cast me aside?

507
00:27:34,200 --> 00:27:35,949
We still don't know

508
00:27:37,000 --> 00:27:38,590
who will come out on top today.

509
00:27:41,000 --> 00:27:41,949
Someone!

510
00:27:55,640 --> 00:27:56,949
Are you surprised?

511
00:27:58,720 --> 00:28:00,550
While you were in a coma,

512
00:28:01,319 --> 00:28:03,038
I changed most of the guards

513
00:28:03,039 --> 00:28:05,150
to my own people.

514
00:28:14,400 --> 00:28:15,590
Those who resist me,

515
00:28:17,720 --> 00:28:20,429
don't think
about leaving this place alive.

516
00:28:22,519 --> 00:28:25,429
You still won't
reflect on your mistakes.

517
00:28:25,519 --> 00:28:26,749
Listen to my command.

518
00:28:29,200 --> 00:28:30,870
Kill everyone.

519
00:28:47,839 --> 00:28:48,790
Run!

520
00:28:51,359 --> 00:28:52,350
Lord Li,

521
00:28:52,480 --> 00:28:53,909
where are you going?

522
00:28:54,000 --> 00:28:56,500
According to the King of Nanzhao's order,
the palace is sealed.

523
00:28:56,599 --> 00:28:57,870
Those who dare trespass on it

524
00:28:57,960 --> 00:28:59,070
will be killed.

525
00:29:00,039 --> 00:29:00,749
Boss,

526
00:29:00,799 --> 00:29:03,189
this woman is Great Tang's
Commandery Princess Consort An.

527
00:29:03,319 --> 00:29:04,110
Capture her!

528
00:29:04,559 --> 00:29:05,350
Stop!

529
00:29:11,759 --> 00:29:13,269
Eldest Princess Consort is here!

530
00:29:13,359 --> 00:29:14,509
Who dares to cause trouble?

531
00:29:18,839 --> 00:29:20,870
You Chen'an's rebellion
has been spoiled.

532
00:29:21,359 --> 00:29:24,310
We are here on the King's orders
to kill all his remnants.

533
00:29:24,640 --> 00:29:27,229
Put down your sword
and your life will be spared.

534
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:29,318
Otherwise, all of you will be killed!

535
00:29:29,319 --> 00:29:30,630
- Killed!
- Killed!

536
00:29:46,119 --> 00:29:47,870
Today, let us

537
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:52,030
end things here.

538
00:29:55,640 --> 00:29:56,518
You Chen'an,

539
00:29:56,519 --> 00:29:57,310
stop!

540
00:30:06,839 --> 00:30:07,989
Stop?

541
00:30:10,039 --> 00:30:11,790
How can I stop?

542
00:30:14,279 --> 00:30:15,269
Who has cared about me

543
00:30:16,519 --> 00:30:18,239
in this world?

544
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,269
Your mother!

545
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:24,350
She endured all kinds of humiliation

546
00:30:24,680 --> 00:30:26,310
and suffered in life

547
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,590
just so her son

548
00:30:28,920 --> 00:30:30,229
can live a stable life

549
00:30:30,839 --> 00:30:32,429
so she can rest in peace

550
00:30:33,079 --> 00:30:34,509
in the underworld.

551
00:30:35,559 --> 00:30:37,469
But look at you now!

552
00:30:38,519 --> 00:30:40,310
Is this what she wanted to see

553
00:30:40,640 --> 00:30:41,949
after going through so much?

554
00:30:44,279 --> 00:30:45,269
Be careful, it's hot.

555
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:48,429
Much better than when I am around.

556
00:30:50,400 --> 00:30:51,709
Your Highness, you are my...

557
00:30:58,599 --> 00:30:59,870
Let him go.

558
00:31:02,200 --> 00:31:03,110
King of Nanzhao.

559
00:31:04,839 --> 00:31:07,550
You Chen'an committed
many crimes in Great Tang.

560
00:31:07,599 --> 00:31:09,350
He might be spared in Nanzhao,

561
00:31:10,440 --> 00:31:12,269
but as the Censor of Great Tang,

562
00:31:12,917 --> 00:31:14,787
I must bring him back to Great Tang,

563
00:31:14,839 --> 00:31:16,030
to be judged.

564
00:31:16,759 --> 00:31:17,709
Commandery Prince An,

565
00:31:18,640 --> 00:31:20,709
I've lost one of my sons.

566
00:31:21,599 --> 00:31:24,189
This is already out of my control

567
00:31:24,487 --> 00:31:26,397
and I've reaped what I sown.

568
00:31:26,799 --> 00:31:27,949
But Chen'an is...

569
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:29,310
He is...

570
00:31:30,279 --> 00:31:33,390
He is my only hope, after all.

571
00:31:33,839 --> 00:31:35,030
All the crimes

572
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,590
he committed,

573
00:31:36,839 --> 00:31:39,558
I'll agree with all kinds
of punishments from Great Tang.

574
00:31:39,559 --> 00:31:41,909
As long as you spare his life.

575
00:31:43,519 --> 00:31:45,150
Spare my life?

576
00:31:45,319 --> 00:31:46,399
Nanzhao

577
00:31:46,400 --> 00:31:48,469
will agree with all kinds of conditions

578
00:31:48,599 --> 00:31:50,669
suggested by Great Tang.

579
00:31:52,630 --> 00:31:54,550
I've encountered
two good things in the capital.

580
00:31:54,839 --> 00:31:55,669
One,

581
00:31:55,880 --> 00:31:57,709
getting to meet He.

582
00:31:57,960 --> 00:31:59,949
Two, getting to know His Highness.

583
00:32:01,039 --> 00:32:02,479
However, to have

584
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:04,469
one of the best coroners as my teacher,

585
00:32:04,839 --> 00:32:06,229
I'm really very fortunate.

586
00:32:06,720 --> 00:32:07,509
I believe

587
00:32:07,799 --> 00:32:08,749
you will

588
00:32:09,119 --> 00:32:10,709
one day become

589
00:32:11,039 --> 00:32:12,390
the greatest coroner in the world.

590
00:32:18,960 --> 00:32:20,909
I was happiest

591
00:32:22,319 --> 00:32:24,030
when I was at the Three Judicial Offices.

592
00:32:24,839 --> 00:32:25,709
Chu Chu,

593
00:32:27,799 --> 00:32:28,989
I'm very happy

594
00:32:30,240 --> 00:32:31,550
to have you as my mentor.

595
00:32:35,119 --> 00:32:36,110
Xiao Jinyu,

596
00:32:39,960 --> 00:32:41,269
it is my honor

597
00:32:43,759 --> 00:32:45,070
to be your opponent.

598
00:32:49,160 --> 00:32:51,150
I envy both of you.

599
00:32:53,240 --> 00:32:55,870
You have a group of friends
who share the same ambition.

600
00:32:57,119 --> 00:32:59,269
It's a thing of happiness.

601
00:33:04,960 --> 00:33:05,909
Father,

602
00:33:10,039 --> 00:33:11,269
I don't deserve

603
00:33:13,200 --> 00:33:14,150
to wear this robe.

604
00:33:16,759 --> 00:33:18,110
You were in control

605
00:33:19,359 --> 00:33:20,669
of my life at birth,

606
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:22,749
but it will be

607
00:33:25,000 --> 00:33:26,790
in my control at death!

608
00:33:29,400 --> 00:33:31,429
Chen'an!

609
00:33:34,319 --> 00:33:35,870
- My King!
- My King!

610
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:44,949
(What have I been seeking
all these years?)

611
00:34:17,000 --> 00:34:18,879
The King of Nanzhao
did not go back on his word.

612
00:34:18,880 --> 00:34:20,510
He agreed to all our conditions.

613
00:34:21,930 --> 00:34:23,829
Both his princes
passed away one after another.

614
00:34:23,960 --> 00:34:25,389
I think he can no longer focus

615
00:34:25,559 --> 00:34:27,510
on palace matters.

616
00:34:29,599 --> 00:34:31,309
Why haven't
Chu Chu and Leng Yue returned?

617
00:34:31,800 --> 00:34:33,150
I've let everyone settle down.

618
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:38,669
Chu Chu just escaped death

619
00:34:38,679 --> 00:34:40,990
and she's already treating patients.

620
00:34:41,159 --> 00:34:43,359
The patients who have
the bugs removed from their gut

621
00:34:43,360 --> 00:34:44,829
are all in good shape.

622
00:34:44,830 --> 00:34:47,390
There won't be a problem
as long as they apply medicine on time.

623
00:34:47,400 --> 00:34:49,190
Chief Clerk Han is
taking care of them over there.

624
00:34:50,320 --> 00:34:52,269
Nanzhao's rebellion has been quelled.

625
00:34:52,599 --> 00:34:54,999
Let's pack up
and report back to His Majesty.

626
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:56,279
Jiaozhou has nice scenery

627
00:34:56,280 --> 00:34:57,630
and I finally get to come out.

628
00:34:57,800 --> 00:34:59,829
I have no official position anyway.

629
00:35:00,280 --> 00:35:02,269
I plan to stay here
for a couple of days.

630
00:35:02,519 --> 00:35:03,749
If my wife is staying,

631
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:04,229
I...

632
00:35:06,199 --> 00:35:07,430
Who is your wife?

633
00:35:09,920 --> 00:35:11,910
Vice Minister Jing,

634
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:14,190
have you forgotten about
the divorce letter someone wrote?

635
00:35:14,639 --> 00:35:16,789
I am single now.

636
00:35:19,840 --> 00:35:21,590
Dear, I'm well-prepared.

637
00:35:21,719 --> 00:35:24,070
I prepared these betrothal gifts
before I left the capital.

638
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:26,359
I have everything

639
00:35:26,360 --> 00:35:27,709
and they are all the best.

640
00:35:33,800 --> 00:35:34,749
Yue,

641
00:35:35,280 --> 00:35:36,189
I came today

642
00:35:36,199 --> 00:35:37,789
to propose.

643
00:35:38,159 --> 00:35:40,269
Since marrying you, I realized

644
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:42,158
it's not enough

645
00:35:42,159 --> 00:35:43,430
being alone.

646
00:35:43,559 --> 00:35:44,389
Yue,

647
00:35:44,559 --> 00:35:45,430
trust me.

648
00:35:46,519 --> 00:35:48,309
No matter what happens in the future,

649
00:35:48,440 --> 00:35:50,510
I will do my best to love you.

650
00:35:51,199 --> 00:35:53,110
Can you give me another chance?

651
00:35:58,050 --> 00:35:59,550
Our fate is over

652
00:35:59,679 --> 00:36:00,590
in this life.

653
00:36:12,039 --> 00:36:12,990
However,

654
00:36:17,039 --> 00:36:18,789
when we tied our hair
during our marriage,

655
00:36:19,159 --> 00:36:20,389
we made three knots.

656
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:23,150
Each knot represents one life.

657
00:36:23,920 --> 00:36:24,950
That means

658
00:36:25,199 --> 00:36:26,550
there are two more lives.

659
00:36:28,559 --> 00:36:30,349
In the next two lives,

660
00:36:31,320 --> 00:36:32,789
I hope you

661
00:36:33,159 --> 00:36:36,189
live each day carefully,
Vice Minister Jing.

662
00:36:37,559 --> 00:36:38,590
She agreed!

663
00:36:38,880 --> 00:36:41,470
She agreed!

664
00:36:42,920 --> 00:36:44,959
She agreed!

665
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:46,829
Chu Chu and His Highness are watching.

666
00:36:48,960 --> 00:36:50,238
Let's go.

667
00:36:50,239 --> 00:36:51,090
Jing Yi.

668
00:36:56,360 --> 00:36:58,309
A life of peace without war

669
00:36:58,760 --> 00:37:00,430
is a good thing for the kingdom.

670
00:37:01,519 --> 00:37:03,030
Nanzhao is hurt

671
00:37:03,239 --> 00:37:05,229
and Great Tang has recovered.

672
00:37:06,119 --> 00:37:07,829
Our hard work did not go in vain.

673
00:37:09,079 --> 00:37:10,789
In the past, I've never imagined

674
00:37:11,159 --> 00:37:12,869
a small coroner like me

675
00:37:13,440 --> 00:37:15,630
could do so many things for Great Tang.

676
00:37:16,280 --> 00:37:18,349
Now, I just hope
to return to the capital soon

677
00:37:18,350 --> 00:37:20,598
and set the coroner examination
and recruitment in motion

678
00:37:20,599 --> 00:37:23,150
to help Great Tang choose more coroners.

679
00:37:25,840 --> 00:37:27,510
I'm afraid you can't do that now.

680
00:37:28,000 --> 00:37:29,959
Did something urgent happen again?

681
00:37:29,960 --> 00:37:30,950
It is very important.

682
00:37:34,520 --> 00:37:35,910
We've been married for three years

683
00:37:36,079 --> 00:37:38,269
and you haven't accompanied me.

684
00:37:39,639 --> 00:37:41,430
Now that we've settled everything,

685
00:37:41,719 --> 00:37:44,510
I wonder if you are willing
to take a leave of absence

686
00:37:44,840 --> 00:37:47,389
and travel with me?

687
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:54,349
Harmony between husband and wife
is very important.

688
00:37:54,679 --> 00:37:57,789
In that case, I'll reluctantly agree.

689
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:10,090
♪I ask time itself to hold the pen
and write the ending of eternity♪

690
00:38:14,079 --> 00:38:15,590
The sun feels nice today.

691
00:38:19,639 --> 00:38:21,150
Everything is nice.

692
00:38:32,500 --> 00:38:35,238
(Upright and Noble)

693
00:38:35,239 --> 00:38:37,470
After Chen'an's rebellion,

694
00:38:37,760 --> 00:38:39,749
Nanzhao has been dealt a serious blow.

695
00:38:40,639 --> 00:38:43,510
Business in Chang'an
has returned to normal.

696
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:46,309
Great Tang can finally recuperate.

697
00:38:47,199 --> 00:38:49,349
All of you have stood up

698
00:38:49,559 --> 00:38:50,990
and risked your lives

699
00:38:51,519 --> 00:38:53,349
when the state is in a crisis

700
00:38:53,519 --> 00:38:55,389
to deal with Nanzhao's scheme.

701
00:38:55,760 --> 00:38:58,550
All of you are
the pillars of Great Tang.

702
00:38:59,119 --> 00:39:00,630
We are willing

703
00:39:00,840 --> 00:39:02,110
to sacrifice our lives

704
00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:03,389
for Your Majesty.

705
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:05,550
I'm not afraid to face hardship

706
00:39:05,599 --> 00:39:06,910
and serve the public

707
00:39:07,039 --> 00:39:07,950
to help Your Majesty

708
00:39:07,960 --> 00:39:09,110
resolve any problems.

709
00:39:11,679 --> 00:39:12,510
Jinbao,

710
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:13,709
issue the decree.

711
00:39:13,760 --> 00:39:14,470
Yes.

712
00:39:14,900 --> 00:39:19,739
♪A twisted path, rising and falling,
seek the path amid the hazy unknown♪

713
00:39:19,740 --> 00:39:24,399
♪Writing oblivion with a sharp blade♪

714
00:39:24,400 --> 00:39:27,550
Commandery Princess Consort An,
Yun Chu Chu, from Qianzhou.

715
00:39:27,600 --> 00:39:29,780
The Court of Judicial Review's
Vice Minister, Jing Yi.

716
00:39:30,000 --> 00:39:32,550
Qianzhongdao's Leng Yue.

717
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:34,110
In the journey to Jiaozhou,

718
00:39:34,119 --> 00:39:36,349
with your fearlessness in danger,
tireless dedication,

719
00:39:36,519 --> 00:39:38,030
and unmatched courage,

720
00:39:38,119 --> 00:39:39,759
you saved the people in times of danger

721
00:39:39,760 --> 00:39:41,829
and rescued the state from disaster.

722
00:39:41,960 --> 00:39:43,789
You will stand as an example to all.

723
00:39:44,480 --> 00:39:47,518
Commandery Prince An, Xiao Jinyu,
quelled the unrest at Nanzhao.

724
00:39:47,519 --> 00:39:48,759
For your distinguished accomplishments

725
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:50,310
and the exceptional favor
you have merited,

726
00:39:50,320 --> 00:39:53,269
you will be bestowed an iron certificate
engraved with a golden bell.

727
00:39:53,270 --> 00:39:55,038
May you continue in unity
and exert all your efforts

728
00:39:55,039 --> 00:39:56,359
to achieve further extraordinary merit.

729
00:39:56,360 --> 00:39:57,950
That's all!

730
00:39:58,079 --> 00:39:59,749
- Yes.
- Yes.

731
00:39:59,750 --> 00:40:01,880
- Thank you, Your Majesty.
- Thank you, Your Majesty.

732
00:40:02,020 --> 00:40:07,250
♪Fearing no wild lands, I press on♪

733
00:40:07,420 --> 00:40:13,019
♪To see the tides of the world
once more♪

734
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:17,939
♪The deeper truth is buried, it grows♪

735
00:40:17,940 --> 00:40:21,250
♪Until it is set free♪

736
00:40:32,100 --> 00:40:35,410
(The End)

737
00:40:50,620 --> 00:40:53,660
♪Time drips away
like fading crimson scent♪

738
00:40:53,660 --> 00:40:57,180
♪The hardships of arrival pass
in a fleeting blink♪

739
00:40:57,540 --> 00:41:00,300
♪Palm lines carry
the footprints of memory♪

740
00:41:00,780 --> 00:41:04,260
♪Leading us out of every winding turn♪

741
00:41:05,100 --> 00:41:08,900
♪If two hearts can fly as one
then storms are part of the way♪

742
00:41:08,900 --> 00:41:12,180
♪Looking back the sky
has already cleared♪

743
00:41:12,300 --> 00:41:14,820
♪Your branches entwined with mine♪

744
00:41:14,820 --> 00:41:18,220
♪Bound together in mutual reliance♪

745
00:41:20,340 --> 00:41:23,420
♪Rugged roads become
the paths of sun and moon♪

746
00:41:23,420 --> 00:41:26,500
♪Fireflies like stars circle
through the seasons♪

747
00:41:27,340 --> 00:41:29,460
♪Shining with the hope of dreams♪

748
00:41:29,460 --> 00:41:34,140
♪This world is no longer in rags♪

749
00:41:34,860 --> 00:41:38,500
♪Only by holding you in my heart
do I dare embrace fear♪

750
00:41:38,500 --> 00:41:41,780
♪Quietly waiting for rumors to fade♪

751
00:41:42,180 --> 00:41:44,500
♪Together we face the tides of fate♪

752
00:41:44,500 --> 00:41:48,660
♪Turning the course of heaven and earth♪

753
00:41:48,780 --> 00:41:51,380
♪This love was never easy♪

754
00:41:51,380 --> 00:41:55,780
♪So life and death will not part us♪

755
00:41:56,140 --> 00:41:58,700
♪Like sinking into the deep sea♪

756
00:41:58,700 --> 00:42:03,700
♪The first breath upon awakening♪

757
00:42:03,700 --> 00:42:05,940
♪This bond will never waver♪

758
00:42:05,940 --> 00:42:10,820
♪So we stay together
till our hair turns white♪

759
00:42:10,820 --> 00:42:13,300
♪I ask time itself to hold the pen♪

760
00:42:13,300 --> 00:42:18,340
♪And write the ending of eternity♪

761
00:42:18,380 --> 00:42:20,660
♪This love was never easy♪

762
00:42:20,660 --> 00:42:24,820
♪So I believe without doubt♪

763
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:28,060
♪Like a thousand sails passing by♪

764
00:42:28,060 --> 00:42:32,980
♪Reaching shore
at the first light of dawn♪

765
00:42:33,460 --> 00:42:35,340
♪This bond will never waver♪

766
00:42:35,340 --> 00:42:40,340
♪So joy and sorrow
are no longer ours to choose♪

767
00:42:40,340 --> 00:42:42,740
♪I will prove it
with the rest of my life♪

768
00:42:42,740 --> 00:42:48,500
♪Together at the edge
of the world without an end♪
